#**NERDMCDUCK INDUSTRIES**

### Welcome to NerdMcDuck Industries
At NerdMcDuck Industries we try our best to achieve world domination in the fastest and simplest way possible. Below you will find steps on how to achieve World Domination. Not interested in world domination? We also offer advice in tri-state area domination. 

### A fundamental Rule
Trust **NO ONE**
Such an important step in the process of World Domination. This is probably the most fundamental rule because once someone figures out what you're up to, they either; want to join you or stop you from achieving your goal. They may even want to stall you. Now onto the steps.

### Listing Steps, Please wait...
![Image](http://www.mytreedb.com/uploads/mytreedb/loader/ajax_loader_blue_64.gif)


### You listed the steps, now what?
It is up to you to decide whether to follow them or not. Here at NerdMcDuck Industries, we strive to transition our customers from regular folks to world domination leaders as swiftly and smoothly as possible. If you need help following these steps, or don't know how to go about performing these steps, please don't hesitate to contact our World Domination Hotline. Standard rates apply, conquering the world isn't free you know. 

### Support or Contact
If none of these methods work then no worries! We got you covered. We'll send a NerdMcDuck representative to your location as soon as humanly possible.
